<item>
            <title>[SPR-938] implementing different types of advices in the same class does not work</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-938</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when implementing more than one advice interface (AfterReturningAdvice, ThrowsAdvice or MethodBeforeAdvice) only one of the hook method gets invoked.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
